{"tid":1347383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府利用黑勢力施行恐襲 及 分區戒嚴","createTime":"2019-07-22T05:59:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T07:25:39.000Z","uid":54125,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1ac569eaed776946ad8286c6b0b272c2a0e0fbac","tid":1347383,"uid":54125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:59:31.000Z","msg":"睇到呢兩單，我相信朋友消息係真嘅<br />\n<br />\n沙田馬鞍友今晚小心！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1347070\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1347070</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n屯門市中心好多鋪頭突然關門........<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1347108\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1347108</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n朋友收到警察親戚通知<br />\n指學生會喺今日下午4點到元朗，8點到屯門搞事<br />\n叫朋友早啲返屋企<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>有理由相信政府正運用警黑<br />\n以施行恐怖襲擊方式實行分區戒嚴<br />\n配合傳言將責任歸於示威者</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n由沙田開始已經係發展至 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>國家向平民恐襲事件</strong></span></span><br />\n各位請一齊議定對應方法<br />\n及向國際由此方向進行文宣"},{"pid":"a447f36ecad908c975e5d0950be4b970ffb089ed","tid":1347383,"uid":54125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:59:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"28b5804863006fdda4f91bd1ff98c123ea6fb052","tid":1347383,"uid":54125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:00:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c87993e662026ad4068120026e5f686a916e3b65","tid":1347383,"uid":54125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:00:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"23e731bb8aff497bf8ad44367b44643c43e7e873","tid":1347383,"uid":5550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:00:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s3.gifyu.com/images/SmartSelect_20190722-113914_Chrome.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3.gifyu.com%2Fimages%2FSmartSelect_20190722-113914_Chrome.gif&h=6c7